:", and installation of this payload occurs after enrolling with MDM in Setup Assistant, the system requests Setup Assistant to enable FileVault at setup time.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"To use this, enable the Await Device Configured DEP configuration option and send this profile with this key set, before sending the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc://com.apple.devicemanagement/documentation/DeviceManagement/DeviceConfiguredCommand"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"An admin SecureToken user is required, otherwise the FileVault pane does not appear.","type":"text"}]}]},{"required":false,"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The path to the location of the recovery key and computer information property list.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"OutputPath","type":[{"kind":"text","text":"string"}],"introducedVersion":"10.9.0","attributes":[]},{"attributes":[],"required":false,"introducedVersion":"10.9.0","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The password of the Open Directory user to add to FileVault. Use the "},{"code":"UserEntersMissingInfo","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" key to prompt for this information.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"Password","type":[{"kind":"text","text":"string"}]},{"type":[{"text":"string","kind":"text"}],"attributes":[],"introducedVersion":"10.9.0","name":"PayloadCertificateUUID","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The UUID of the payload within the same profile containing the asymmetric recovery key certificate payload.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"required":false},{"type":[{"kind":"text","text":"boolean"}],"introducedVersion":"10.9.0","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"code":"false","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", the system prevents display of the personal recovery key to the user after the system enables FileVault.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph